### Global ignores for ESchool monorepo

## OS / editor
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.vscode/
.idea/
*.iml

## Environment / secrets
.env
.env.*.local
*.env
*.local

## Root-level dependency / build artifacts (if ever created here)
/node_modules/
/dist/
/build/

## Backend (Spring Boot) artifacts
/backend/target/
/backend/.mvn/wrapper/maven-wrapper.jar
/backend/.idea/
/backend/.classpath
/backend/.project
/backend/.settings/

## Frontend (Vue) artifacts
/frontend/node_modules/
/frontend/dist/
/frontend/dist-ssr/
/frontend/coverage/
/frontend/.eslintcache

## Logs
*.log
logs/

## JVM crash logs
hs_err_pid*
replay_pid*
